{
  "texts": [
    "Furthermore, it should not be overlooked that there are still some limitations in this study, as it was limited to literature samples published in the Scopus database, and only includes journal articles written in English.",
    "Consequently, some publications that are indexed in other databases (e.g., Web of Science), written in other languages (e.g., Chinese), and other types of sources (e.g., conference proceedings) could be omitted.",
    "Moreover, it is conceivable that the keywords used in the litera-ture search might not completely encompass the subject matter.",
    "Additional keywords could be included in future research."
  ]
}